72 720 Td
(Answer: 327) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Solution:) Tj
T*
(The process involves: 1 RTT for TCP handshake, 1 RTT for the base HTML file, and 6 RTTs) Tj
T*
(for the 6 images \(since there is no pipelining, each object requires its own RTT\). Total) Tj
T*
(RTTs = 1 + 1 + 6 = 8. Total RTT time = 8 * 40ms = 320ms. There are 7 objects total \(1) Tj
T*
(HTML + 6 images\), each with a transmission time of 1ms. Total transmission time = 7 *) Tj
T*
(1ms = 7ms. Total time = 320ms + 7ms = 327ms.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Question 4) Tj
T*
(Consider a link with a distance of 4,000 km and a propagation speed of 2 * 10^8 m/s. The) Tj
T*
(bandwidth of the link is 100 Mbps. Calculate the total delay in milliseconds) Tj
T*
(\(propagation + transmission\) for a single packet of size 1,250,000 bytes.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Answer: 120) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Solution:) Tj
T*
(Propagation delay = Distance / Speed = 4,000,000 m / \(2 * 10^8 m/s\) = 0.02 seconds = 20) Tj
T*
(ms. Transmission delay = Packet Size / Bandwidth = \(1,250,000 bytes * 8 bits/byte\) /) Tj
T*
(100,000,000 bps = 10,000,000 / 100,000,000 = 0.1 seconds = 100 ms. Total delay = 20 ms +) Tj
T*
(100 ms = 120 ms.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Question 5) Tj
T*
(Explain the difference between persistent connections with pipelining and persistent) Tj
T*
(connections without pipelining in HTTP/1.1. Specifically, how does pipelining affect the) Tj
T*
(number of RTTs required to fetch N objects after the base HTML file is received?) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Answer: Without pipelining, the client must wait for a response before sending the next) Tj
T*
(request, resulting in N RTTs for N objects. With pipelining, the client sends requests) Tj
T*
(for all N objects back-to-back as soon as they are identified, ideally resulting in only) Tj
T*
(1 RTT for all N objects.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Solution:) Tj
T*
(Pipelining allows multiple HTTP requests to be sent over a single TCP connection without) Tj
T*
(waiting for the corresponding responses. This reduces the impact of RTT on the total) Tj
T*
(fetch time for multiple objects.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
ET
